N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 203.5 - Unlawful crossings

State Regulations

No vehicle shall cross, or attempt to cross, any bridge
without the payment of tolls as prescribed by these rules and
regulations. Notes
